e_in_Physics\" title=\"Nobel Prize in Physics\">Nobel Prize in Physics<\/a> in 2001, together with <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Eric_Allin_Cornell\" title=\"Eric Allin Cornell\">Eric Allin Cornell<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Carl_Wieman\" title=\"Carl Wieman\">Carl Wieman<\/a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Wolfgang_Ketterle#cite_note-3\"><span>[<\/span>3<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><\/p>","name":"Wolfgang Ketterle","place_of_birth":"Heidelberg , Germany","place_of_death":null,"text":"Wolfgang Ketterle , Physics, 2001","year":2001.0}